Package: ferroanalysis
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Analysis Tools for Ferroelectric Device Characterization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Badran", "Elshenawy",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "badran.elshenawy@ndm.ox.ac.uk",
    comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")
  )
Description: Provides comprehensive analysis tools for ferroelectric device 
    characterization including time-domain analysis, hysteresis loop extraction,
    current-voltage relationships, voltage partitioning mechanisms, and parametric
    sensitivity studies. Designed for HfO2-based ferroelectric capacitors and 
    other ferroelectric materials with support for automated analysis pipelines
    and publication-ready visualizations.
